song_lyrics: Me to khānte ḍhāḷī vhālā khāṭalḍī,
Ubhī jou chhu tārī vāṭalḍī... māre 1
Maru tan man dhan ek sāthe,
Hu to Mohan vārū laī tam mathe... māre 2
Me to tanḍu dharyu chhe tamne varvā... māre 3
title: Māre mandire padhāro māvā re

metadata.kirtan_info:
1-801: Sadguru Brahmanand Swami
